channel.description:
i dont care if you flame me ... its obvious some of you will its my first server so please be nice here it is..
[B]features[/B] stable econmy new imations gfx and emotes gs stnce 100% ags , bgs , sgs ,zgs spec all 100%l ike rs clan chat works 90% ::ccmake (playername) ::ccjoin (player name) / too speak d claw spec works 100% like rs ive made barrows more effective void works d bolt spec randoly black mask corrupt dragon armour all pvp armour veta , morigan , statius, all gw bosses bandos has got minions. custom boss donator tickets with donator area (custom boses nd shop) new interfaces -pc pking ect [B]pictures ![/B] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/22md7k.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/voquyh.png[/img] quests work but you dont have too do em :D [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/1z2zkfs.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2v277m0.png[/img]
the old name was corrupt pk but no changed too ps-revolution:D cuz corrupt pk sucked.
change ip in client too connect to your servers ip or local host.
server: [URL=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=LRJ968WR]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=LRJ968WR[/URL] client: [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=FJ3DM56D]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=FJ3DM56D[/url]
credits: me elite pk delta bluur others enjoy constructive critism would be nice but if cant post that just flam .. if need any help editing anyhtink just post here ill be happy too help.
